        <p>In addition to selecting a file type from the list, you can type the file type extension in the field directly. This can be especially useful for file types not included in the drop-down. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare">For example, if you want to look in all target files in the project, you can type <span class="TypedEntry">*.fltar</span> in the field.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
